I have made this several times. It is a beautiful dessert and is very impressive in appearance though extremely easy to make. I used the zest of one lemon to the cream cheese mixture. In my opinion, it just needs this. I also used Trader Joe's blueberry preserves because that's what I had and it was just terrific. It is hard to eat without messing it up. Make it, you'll see...but it is very yummy and easy.

